---
title: Chinese Glazed Roast Chicken with Ginger-Peanut Rice and Spicy Sauce
description: Succulent roast chicken lacquered in a glaze reminiscent of Chinese BBQ.  Drizzle the sweet and spicy sauce over everything!   Crunchy peanut rice brings this whole dish together for a winner winner chicken dinner!
